featured_reviews.review_id:
From my experience I can say Some of the sweetest memories are started from here .
Because, Going back to flashback I came to here for pray  purpose during end of Ramzaan 
During 2000'$ Eidgah is very vast but then after 2016 Getting update slowly.
After 2020 Dimensions like Minar, fencing wall , Entrance Gate is constructed.
Apart from this, Childhood day's like 10th class my friends come here to play cricket 
This place is soo crucial for animals habitation too
We celebrate here festival  as Ramadan Mubarak, Eid al Adha etc.
Over Some Thousands of people  visit here which is happening yearly twice.
 Unbelievable this place can't forget this place Easily .
This place is soo favourite and too sacred because if home  village get any problem come here just pray then the problem solved itself that's the power of this place.
Hope this place as love as possible
